2.19.21  6:36 am   hi i saw somebody interview you on her for their art class and i need to interview a musician or aspiring musician for music class so i'm copying their idea
1. what's your biggest goal when it comes to your music?

     figure out how reality works, and share my findings with others

      2. why do you think people enjoy music so much?

     if the person making it has done a good job

     3. what's one necessary step every musician must take to further advance their career?

     enjoy music at least once

      songwriting

      i'm not sure

2.19.21  12:37 am   how did you become really awesome

      i have a list of non-awesome things, and i try to never do those things. or at least if i do, then i try to release a propaganda video right away saying that i didn't

2.18.21  10:05 pm   Do facts care about your feelings?

      they care about the feelings of the person who is delivering the fact. not necessarily anyone else

2.18.21  9:25 pm   Do you ever write songs whilst dreaming?

      yes

2.18.21  6:27 pm   how to make music?

      i was going to say no but now that i think about it yes

2.18.21  5:46 pm   do all of your songs take place in the same universe? 

      they all can take place in your imagination

2.18.21  4:37 pm   Do you think that time is rigid (there is one and only one future and it cannot be changed) or malleable (there are infinite possibilities and we can't predict our future) ?

      malleable

2.18.21  4:22 pm   I've noticed some of your music isn't recorded at 440 hertz. What hertz are you using and why?

      the tuning i use is A=440hz. the reason i use that is because everyone uses it

2.18.21  3:52 pm   do u agree that edmonton is kinda like the cincinnati of canada? 

      i was going to say no but now that i think about it yes

2.18.21  3:35 pm   hey bill, do your ideas come on a whim or do you have to think for awhile?

      the best ideas are on whim. if there is no whim, then i'll have to think for a while, but the longer i think the less likely there will be any whim

2.18.21  2:59 pm   whats your favorite music?

      regular

2.18.21  1:44 pm   Can i take "i wanna go outside" as a metafor for coming out of the closet? It fits really well

      it's about the desire to enter a refreshingly more expansive realm

2.18.21  1:09 pm   In the random questions, I see people in late 2019 asking when you are going to upload a new video, and you said you were going to make a countdown timer? What ever happened to that?

      the countdown timer was fake but i was hoping i could will it into existence

2.18.21  12:53 pm   you seem to be very adamant on the fact that you're normal. do you think this is normal?

      no

2.18.21  12:52 pm   in "i can play" what are you referring to that you can play? (ie. music/sport/game etc)

     it's probably about songwriting

     and what was the inspiration behind "i can play"?

     the fresh feeling that you can really stretch out and have some fun, in songwriting

2.18.21  11:45 am   are you a robot

      no

      from the toilet, in the gutter. bet you didn't think they had toilets in the gutter, well here i am, as living proof

      some of the canteloupe ones

      try again

      directly in front of your face
